data.description: This home is move-in ready and just waiting for you!  Enjoy one level living in a quiet comfy setting.  Recently remodeled brick ranch with updated windows, roof, appliances (all in 2020), cabinetry and heat pump! Hardwood floors throughout most of the home and tiled kitchen and bathrooms; huge garage/workshop on over one acre.
